                </div>

                    <p style="text-align: center;"><span class="ff-40-
purple"><i aria-hidden="true" class="fa fa-user">&nbsp;</i></span></p>

<p>Rett syndrome is named after&nbsp;<strong><span class="ff-purple">Andreas Rett</span></strong>, an Austrian physician who published the first description of the condition in 1966.</p>


